// Replace 192.168.0.50 with your API server LAN IP if testing outside Docker
### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Heartbeat
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/heartbeat
Authorization: Bearer KEY1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bot_id": "bot-1",
  "spread": 12,
  "equity": 1000,
  "features": {"rsi": 48, "atr": 0.0007, "session": "LDN"}
}

### Decision
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/decisions/next?bot_id=bot-1
Authorization: Bearer KEY1

### Execution (opened)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/executions
Authorization: Bearer KEY1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decision_id": "REPLACE_WITH_DECISION_UUID",
  "bot_id": "bot-1",
  "status": "OPENED",
  "order_ticket": 1234567,
  "entry_price": 1.12345
}

### Execution (closed)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/executions
Authorization: Bearer KEY1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decision_id": "REPLACE_WITH_DECISION_UUID",
  "bot_id": "bot-1",
  "status": "CLOSED",
  "exit_price": 1.12420,
  "pnl": 7.5,
  "mfe": 12.0,
  "mae": -3.0
}

### Train model (after you have data)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/train?key=changeme-admin
